anism\nis explained within Lagrangian Perturbation Theory and well captured by our\nsimulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Sep 2020 00:50:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2020 17:27:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
