luate our technique for search, MapReduce, and\nclassification functions, and infer how sensitive the processing factor for\neach computation task to the entropic surjectivity is.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Sep 2020 15:42:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-29"}
