n can be solved in $\\mathcal{O}^{\\star}(\\min\\{2.85^k\n\\cdot 8.54^\\ell,2.7^k \\cdot 36.61^\\ell,3^k \\cdot 1.78^\\ell\\})$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 26 Sep 2020 19:04:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
